title: University of Cambridge
description: The University of Cambridge utilizes a diverse palette of vibrant colors to represent its prestigious institution. These colors, sourced from the official identity guidelines document, are emblematic of the university's rich history and modern outlook. The color palette includes shades such as the bold D6083B, striking 0072CF, warm EA7125, refreshing 55A51C, elegant 8F2BBC, and the cool-toned 00B1C1.
